SELECT
  time_bucket('$resolution', time) AS "time",
  slice_total_time as "slice total time",
  packets,
  bytes,
  slice_start_time as "slice start time",
  buffers,
  buffer_parsing_time as "buffer parsing time",
  full_process_time as "full processing time",
  tcp_nodes as "sessions",
  analytics_tag.thread,
  avg_process_time as "average processing time",
  timing_errors
   
FROM analytics join analytics_tag on analytics.tag_id=analytics_tag.tag_id
WHERE
  $__timeFilter("time")
ORDER BY 1

SELECT
  "time" AS "time",
  buffers as "values",
  format('thread %s',analytics_tag.thread)
   
FROM analytics join analytics_tag on analytics.tag_id=analytics_tag.tag_id
WHERE
  analytics_tag.thread != 'shared'::varchar and
  $__timeFilter("time")
ORDER BY 1

SELECT
  "time" AS "time",

  format('active_sessions: %s',analytics_tag.thread)

WHERE

  $__timeFilter("time")
ORDER BY 1

SELECT
  time_bucket('$resolution', time) AS "time",
    (
    CASE
      WHEN bytes_captured >= lag(bytes_captured) OVER w
        THEN bytes_captured - lag(bytes_captured) OVER w
      WHEN lag(bytes_captured) OVER w IS NULL THEN NULL
      ELSE bytes_captured
    END
  ) * 8 / extract(epoch from time - lag(time) OVER w) AS "Throughput",
  (
    CASE
      WHEN packets_captured >= lag(packets_captured) OVER w
        THEN packets_captured - lag(packets_captured) OVER w
      WHEN lag(packets_captured) OVER w IS NULL THEN NULL
      ELSE packets_captured
    END
  ) / extract(epoch from time - lag(time) OVER w) AS "Packets per second"
FROM capture
WHERE
  $__timeFilter("time")
WINDOW w AS (ORDER BY time)
ORDER BY 1

SELECT
  "time" AS "time",(
    CASE
      WHEN packets_dropped >= lag(packets_dropped) OVER w
        THEN packets_dropped - lag(packets_dropped) OVER w
      WHEN lag(packets_dropped) OVER w IS NULL THEN NULL
      ELSE packets_dropped
    END
  ) * 8 / extract(epoch from time - lag(time) OVER w) AS "Packets Dropped"
FROM capture
WHERE
  $__timeFilter("time")
WINDOW w AS (ORDER BY time)
ORDER BY 1

SELECT
  "time" AS "time",
  max(enqueued_errors_target_0_1) as "errors",
  max(enqueued_target_0_1) as "total enqueues",
  max(total_forwards) as "forwards"
   
FROM sniffer join sniffer_tag on sniffer.tag_id=sniffer_tag.tag_id
WHERE
  
  $__timeFilter("time")
GROUP BY
  sniffer.time
ORDER BY 1

SELECT
  "time" AS "time",(
    CASE
      WHEN enqueued_errors_target_0_1 >= lag(enqueued_errors_target_0_1) OVER w
        THEN enqueued_errors_target_0_1 - lag(enqueued_errors_target_0_1) OVER w
      WHEN lag(enqueued_errors_target_0_1) OVER w IS NULL THEN NULL
      ELSE enqueued_errors_target_0_1
    END
  ) * 8 / extract(epoch from time - lag(time) OVER w) AS "enqueue errors"
FROM sniffer join sniffer_tag on sniffer.tag_id=sniffer_tag.tag_id
WHERE
  $__timeFilter("time")
WINDOW w AS (ORDER BY time)
ORDER BY 1
